   <p class="midtext">
      As a medium-scale European Consortium funded within the 7th Framework Programme, 
      ADGLASS brings together leading experts of computational materials modelling, experimental    materials research and glass product manufacturing.
      <br><br>
      Our work aims at improving the quality, efficiency and reliability of interfaces between glassy materials, to develop custom solutions 
      for applications in protein-based drug storage and solar energy collection.
